            "text": "<p>We ship worldwide, making sure that 99% of paid expedited orders are sent within 1 business day, and economy shipping orders are processed within 2 business days.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_3xRxN6": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is the processing and shipping time of an order?",
            "text": "<p>Orders are typically processed within 3-7 business days. Standard shipping within the U.S. takes 3-5 business days, while international shipping times vary depending on the destination. In addition, expedited shipping options are available for faster delivery.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_jUhkWG": {
