            "text": "<p>We may ship your order in multiple packages if items are being fulfilled from different locations or if an item is temporarily out of stock. It will be shipped separately as soon as it becomes available.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_in4ct9": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
